understand in the core of your being if you want to be a great communicator versus just

00:08:42.440 --> 00:08:47.880
have one good communication and always starting from scratch. Threshold concepts are really

00:08:47.880 --> 00:08:52.119
transformative. They really change the way you think and the way you behave once you understand

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:58.599
them. What else? They cross the discipline. So you'll see them popping up in lots of ways.

