And so we really consider speaking to be social. There's an audience to consider,

00:12:13.080 --> 00:12:19.320
what are you trying to do to that audience? And the audience makes the meaning, like a different

00:12:19.320 --> 00:12:24.200
audience is going to change the kind of information you want to share. But it also includes the idea

