that speaking is rhetorical. And that's a, like a fancy jargony word, but really it means that

00:12:30.039 --> 00:12:37.320
you are doing it for a purpose. And it can also include the idea that speaking and speaking words

00:12:37.320 --> 00:12:42.760
out loud is temporal. And even if it's being recorded like this is today, that recording

00:12:42.760 --> 00:12:46.599
is going to be watched at a different time in a different context, and therefore different

00:12:46.599 --> 00:12:56.760
influences will be taking place. The fourth is that speaking is messy. And it took us a second

