And I think that's something to consider. But the other part about speaking being messy includes

00:13:32.919 --> 00:13:38.679
the inherent risk that comes with speaking your thoughts out loud to a group of people that you

00:13:38.679 --> 00:13:43.960
may or may not know. And so there's vulnerability there. And all of those things are tied up in these

00:13:44.119 --> 00:13:53.559
