the feedback is given is really important. And that's why we structure it so carefully to make

00:16:12.679 --> 00:16:17.159
sure that you are getting feedback, the speakers are getting feedback that is valuable and doesn't

00:16:17.159 --> 00:16:21.239
throw them off course and doesn't totally explode their talk at the last minute, which we've seen.

00:16:22.440 --> 00:16:25.960
And so all of those feedback elements are really, really important as well.

